NK041(di)044:1: // kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer gyi gsung thor bu las /
NK041(di)044:2: bar do'i smon lam ngo sprod bzhugs so //
NK041(di)044:4: phyogs dus rgyal ba ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)044:5: bdag gis thog med dus nas da lta'i bar //
NK041(di)044:6: dus gsum bsags dang yod pa'i dge ba des //
NK041(di)044:7: bdag gzhan ma lus byang chub thob par shog /
NK041(di)044:8: de ma thob kyi tshe rabs kun tu yang //
NK041(di)044:9: lam zab rdzogs chen snying po'i don rtogs nas //
NK041(di)044:10: chos nyid mngon sum gong 'phel tshad phebs nas //
NK041(di)044:11: zag bcas phung po 'od skur grol bar shog /
NK041(di)044:12: gnad gcod drag po'i sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK041(di)044:13: bla ma yi dam dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK041(di)044:14: mig gi dbang por mngon sum byon nas ni //
NK041(di)044:15: dbang bskur lung ston mkha' spyod 'khrid par shog /
NK041(di)044:16: 'dus byas mi rtag 'chi ba byung tsa na //
NK041(di)044:17: 'gyu ba'i dbugs chad bems rig bral ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:18: zhen chags 'khrul pa'i snang ba mi 'char bar //
NK041(di)044:19: gnas lugs chos sku'i ngang la gnas par shog /
NK041(di)044:20: sgyu lus gdos bcas 'jog pa'i dus babs na //
NK041(di)044:21: snang phung phra rags rtog pa 'gag pa'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:22: 'khrul med khyab gdal gdod ma'i dbyings chen la //
NK041(di)044:23: bems rig bral ma thag tu grol bar shog /
NK041(di)044:24: ma dag 'byung ba so sor dengs pa'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:25: dag pa'i 'od lnga ma 'dres 'od gsal ngang //
NK041(di)044:26: rtog med 'od lnga'i rdo rje lu gu rgyud //
NK041(di)044:27: dbyer med gcig 'dres chos nyid mthar phyin shog /
NK041(di)044:28: h'u chen khros pa srin po'i gzugs la sogs //
NK041(di)044:29: h'u sgras stong gsum ma lus gang tsa na //
NK041(di)044:30: rig stong h'u sgra'i gnad du ngo shes nas //
NK041(di)044:31: grags stong brag ca lta bur rtogs par shog /
NK041(di)044:32: gshin rje'i gshed ma'i tshogs kyis bskor tsa na //
NK041(di)044:33: rgyob sod 'bros 'ded 'khrul pa dbyings dag nas //
NK041(di)044:34: bred sngangs 'khrul pa'i snang ba mi 'char bar //
NK041(di)044:35: yi dam zhi khro'i sku ru mthong bar shog /
NK041(di)044:36: dung khang 'bar ba'i bde chen gzhal yas nas //
NK041(di)044:37: khro bo'i tshogs rnams gnas nas gyes pa'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:38: 'jigs gzugs srin po'i sku ru mi 'char bar //
NK041(di)044:39: man ngag snying tig dgongs pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK041(di)044:40: tsit+ta rin chen gur khang gzhal yas nas //
NK041(di)044:41: zhi ba'i tshogs rnams dbyings su yal ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:42: snang ba ru log 'od skur shar ba'i dus //
NK041(di)044:43: rig pa 'od kyi klong du thim par shog /
NK041(di)044:44: mgrin mgul rtsa yi 'khor lo bral ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:45: 'jigs pa'i gad rgyangs 'brug stong ldir tsa na /
NK041(di)044:46: +aahmh'u zhi khro'i gdangs su ngo shes nas //
NK041(di)044:47: rig stong skye med sgra ru grol bar shog /
NK041(di)044:48: gsang gnas bde skyong 'khor lo'i gzhal yas nas //
NK041(di)044:49: thabs shes dkar dmar snying gar phrad tsa na //
NK041(di)044:50: bde stong zag pa med pa'i gnas lugs des //
NK041(di)044:51: rlung rig dbu ma'i nang du tshud par shog /
NK041(di)044:52: chos nyid bar do'i ngang la gnas pa'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:53: shes rig lung ma bstan du ma song bar //
NK041(di)044:54: rang grol ka dag chen po'i don rtogs te //
NK041(di)044:55: gzhan stong chos zad ngang la gnas par shog /
NK041(di)044:56: chos nyid mngon sum bden pa mthong ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:57: gnyen po dran 'dzin sgom pa'i blo bral nas //
NK041(di)044:58: ka dag zad sar 'khyol ba'i don rtogs te //
NK041(di)044:59: rtog med spros bral ngang la gnas par shog /
NK041(di)044:60: 'ja' tshon sna lnga 'dres pa'i gzhal yas nas //
NK041(di)044:61: ye shes lnga yi gur khang sgo phye ste //
NK041(di)044:62: sku dang thig les zhing khams gang ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)044:63: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang mjal bar shog /
NK041(di)044:64: thig le stong sgron 'od gsal gzhal yas su //
NK041(di)044:65: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang mjal tsa na //
NK041(di)044:66: snyems byed gnyis snang the tshom med pa ru //
NK041(di)044:67: kun bzang gdod ma'i ngang du thim par shog /
NK041(di)044:68: sems nyid sgron ma bzhi dang dngos mjal nas //
NK041(di)044:69: thig le stong sgron 'od gsal gzhal yas su //
NK041(di)044:70: lhun grub sbubs la brtan pa mthar phyin nas //
NK041(di)044:71: dbyings rig nam mkha'i ngang du 'pho bar shog /
NK041(di)044:72: chos sku stong gsal sgron me 'bar bar shog /
NK041(di)044:73: stong nyid rig pa'i chos sku thob par shog /
NK041(di)044:74: 'gag med gnyis snang longs sku thob par shog /
NK041(di)044:75: rang rig mthar phyin sprul sku thob par shog /
NK041(di)044:76: sku gsum thob nas gzhan don byed par shog //
NK041(di)044:77: ces 'chi kha bar do dang chos nyid bar do'i
NK041(di)044:78: smon lam thos pas grol ba kun mkhyen klong chen
